acp.a:expr: ="Welcome. I'm Joseph Clark, President of " & #"_a-0000d9c4-bcac-8000-9ba2-011c48011c48_6196" & ", a leading supplier of office equipment. You will be using my login to access all aspects of " & #"_a-0000d9c4-bcac-8000-9ba2-011c48011c48_6196" & "'s operations, including our customer and product database, investigations into new business opportunities, handling and responding to unexpected incidents, servicing our customers, and processing new product orders. To login, you'll need to reset my password. I hope you remembered to set the default email addresses to a real email account that you can access. As a reminder, you set the default email for all users to " & pv!defaultEmail & ". To reset my password, you can either use the 'Forgot Password' option on the login screen, or go to the People tab in the designer interface. My login to this system is joseph.clark."
